	abstract = {We are often asked about the scope and purpose of the HealthDCAT-AP–based Health-RI metadata schema. To provide clarity, we distinguish between different types of metadata and their respective functions. Although many categorizations exist, a widely used one groups metadata into three categories: descriptive, structural, and administrative. The latter is sometimes further subdivided into technical, preservation, and rights metadata.

